com.laegler.fastbpmn.fastBpmn

Interface FEvent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, FAbstractElement, FBaseElement, FFlowElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FEventImpl

    public interface FEvent
extends FFlowElement
    A representation of the model object 'FEvent'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Event Type
    • Event Sequence Type
    • Event Handle Type
    • Message
    • Data IO
    • Data Object

    See Also:
    FastBpmnPackage.getFEvent()
